The following (including legal persons) are deemed as ‘related persons’: 

• Officers or directors of one another’s businesses;
• Legally recognised partners in business;
• Employer and employee;
• Any person who directly or indirectly owns, controls or holds twenty-five per cent or more of the outstanding voting stock or shares of both of them;
